     <div type="introduction">
   <pb facs="2"/>
   <p>FYrst: how we maye well &amp; truely answer them, that aske vs, how we know the Byble and the scriptures, to be the worde of god.</p>
   <p n="2">ii. An exposition of all suche places of y<seg rend="sup">e</seg> scriptures, as seme, to adscribe vnto god passiōs of mynde, and humayne lymmes.</p>
   <p n="3">iii. A decleratiō how the masse crepte in fyrste in to the church, and how cleane contrarye to y<seg rend="sup">e</seg> scriptures and holy fathers yt is made a pernitious and dam<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>nable Idoll beyng a very snare and nette inuented by y<seg rend="sup">e</seg> dynell, to catch mens soules, &amp; now by y<seg rend="sup">e</seg> papystes, mayntenyd vpholdē and defendyd to pycke pore mēs pursis.</p>
</div>
